&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Above US $ 10&lt;/b&gt; - Personalized thank you mail from the filmmaker + online access to our final film. &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Above US $ 80&lt;/b&gt; - Personalized thank you mail from the filmmaker + online access to our final film and DVD+ Techung&#039;s latest musical CD, Semshae with autograph + thank you credit at the end of the film. &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Above US $ 250&lt;/b&gt; - Personalized thank you mail from the filmmaker + online access to our final film and DVD + Techung&#039;s latest musical CD, Semshae with autograph + thank you credit at the end of the film + Tshirt especially ordered for the donor. &lt;/li&gt;
